# Snake Game

This project is a modern implementation of the classic Snake game using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript to provide an interactive and fun browser-based experience.

![Snake Game Screenshot](thumbnail.png)

## Features

- Classic Snake gameplay with modern visuals
- Increasing speed as the snake eats apples
- Score and high score tracking with local storage
- Smooth animations and responsive controls
- Deadly walls - don't hit the edges!
- Mobile-friendly touch controls

## Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript (ES6+)
- Canvas API for rendering

## How to Play

1. Open `index.html` in any modern web browser
2. Click "Play" to start the game
3. Use arrow keys or WASD to control the snake's direction
4. On mobile, use the on-screen arrow buttons
5. Eat the red apples to grow the snake and increase your score
6. Avoid hitting walls or colliding with your own tail

## Game Rules

1. Don't hit the walls - they are deadly!
2. Don't eat yourself (collide with your own tail)
3. You can't reverse direction directly
4. The snake speeds up after each apple, increasing the challenge

## High Scores

The game keeps track of your highest score using browser local storage, so your achievements will be saved between sessions.

## Contributing

Contributions are welcome! Feel free to open issues or submit pull requests to improve the game.

